  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Relief Student Care Teacher",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for people, who are passionate about education and nurturing young children, to join our team! If you are cheerful, optimistic and loves children, come join us!</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Positions available: Relief Student Care Teacher for primary school children - English, Chinese, Math & Science ($12 - $14 per hour)</strong></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Manage students and proactively respond to their developmental needs</li><li>Ensure classroom discipline and safety of children at all times</li><li>Deliver and present lesson content to children</li><li>Provide guidance and supervision for Primary School children on the completion of daily homework and spelling</li><li>Assist with other administrative tasks</li><li>Make a difference to our students' developmental years</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements & Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess genuine love to care and mentor children</li><li>WSQ Student Care or qualifications in field of community & social services is an advantage</li><li>Good communication skills and must be team player</li><li>Great sense of responsibility</li></ul><p><strong>Working hours:</strong></p><ul><li>1.30 pm - 6 pm, Mon - Fri</li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please send in your resume. Do include your reasons of leaving, expected salary, last drawn salary and date of availability to commence work.</p><p><br /></p><p>We seek your understanding that only shortlisted candidate will be notified. Thank you.</p>",
